article_title: Massive flooding kills 1, leaves damage in its wake

og.description: Officials said a body was found in a vehicle that had washed into a ravine near Elephant Butte Dam. Meanwhile, flooding Friday ruptured an earthen canal in Las Vegas, N.M., and an aging dam in Southern New Mexico.
